Package it.polimi.ingsw.controller.states

Class GameState

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.controller.states.GameState
Direct Known Subclasses:
DrawCardState, InitializationState, ObjectiveCardSelectionState, PlayCardState, PostGameState, StarterCardSelectionState, TokenSelectionState
public abstract class GameState extends Object
A GameState refers to a state of the gameFlowManager (state machine), implemented using the state pattern. GameState is an abstract class, from which the actual state classes inherit the methods that will eventually be re-implemented
